WEBVTT

01:12:04.390 --> 01:12:08.211
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

01:12:14.222 --> 01:12:17.582
When you seek truth,

01:12:21.262 --> 01:12:23.114
how dynamic one can become,

01:12:23.321 --> 01:12:26.726
you can see the way these artists are,

01:12:27.462 --> 01:12:31.702
how the blessings of the truth helps you

01:12:31.902 --> 01:12:36.799
in your self confidence and in the expression of your art.

01:12:37.782 --> 01:12:42.822
And also you must have seen how the people from the West,

01:12:43.062 --> 01:12:46.702
who have had no training in Indian music which is very difficult,

01:12:46.862 --> 01:12:49.666
how they have taken easily to it.

01:12:49.928 --> 01:12:55.200
In the same way the Indians have taken to Western music very easily.

01:12:56.582 --> 01:12:58.873
The reason is,

01:12:59.064 --> 01:13:02.683
we have to understand what we are.

01:13:04.102 --> 01:13:06.993
And that is the truth one has to know.

01:13:07.194 --> 01:13:13.071
The truth is that you are the Spirit.

01:13:13.990 --> 01:13:17.621
You are not this body, this mind,

01:13:17.822 --> 01:13:22.469
this ego, emotions,

01:13:22.670 --> 01:13:26.022
but you are the Spirit.

01:13:26.222 --> 01:13:29.464
Until you become the Self, Spirit,

01:13:29.665 --> 01:13:34.249
you cannot feel the All-Pervading Power,

01:13:34.409 --> 01:13:37.141
which is very subtle.

01:13:37.342 --> 01:13:41.586
And this is another truth one has to realize,

01:13:41.787 --> 01:13:45.141
that this Power exists

01:13:45.355 --> 01:13:53.279
and it does all the living works,

01:13:54.161 --> 01:13:59.041
it organizes, it thinks,

01:13:59.922 --> 01:14:03.101
above all it loves you.

01:14:03.302 --> 01:14:06.148
But when I say this,

01:14:07.462 --> 01:14:11.782
you have to have an open mind of a scientist.

01:14:12.171 --> 01:14:18.942
If, what I am saying, like a hypothesis,

01:14:19.102 --> 01:14:21.942
turns out to be true,

01:14:22.182 --> 01:14:29.234
then you have to accept it in all your honesty.

01:14:38.622 --> 01:14:40.751
The most important thing today

01:14:40.958 --> 01:14:43.181
is to ask a question to ourselves,

01:14:43.382 --> 01:14:48.481
”Why are we here? What is the purpose of our coming?”

01:14:49.622 --> 01:14:52.359
If we ask such a question

01:14:52.560 --> 01:14:58.137
then only a new search towards the truth will start.

01:14:58.338 --> 01:15:00.902
And these two things that I have told you,

01:15:01.103 --> 01:15:03.910
that you are the Spirit

01:15:04.117 --> 01:15:10.561
and that you have to be in connection with this All-Pervading Power,

01:15:11.196 --> 01:15:13.862
will have to work it out for you

01:15:14.022 --> 01:15:18.102
because then you become the seekers of truth. It's your right.

01:15:18.302 --> 01:15:21.742
So Sahaja means - ‘Saha’ means born with you.

01:15:21.942 --> 01:15:24.911
With - ‘Saha’ is with, ‘Ja’ is born.

01:15:25.094 --> 01:15:27.981
So born with you is the right

01:15:28.182 --> 01:15:32.342
to be united - that is ‘Yoga’ - with this Divine Power.

01:15:32.542 --> 01:15:34.581
This is the real meaning of ‘Yoga’ -

01:15:34.782 --> 01:15:39.639
is that you are to be united with that Divine Power.

01:15:40.780 --> 01:15:45.554
The manifestation of this, when it happens,

01:15:45.755 --> 01:15:50.822
you become a beautiful personality that you are.

01:15:51.022 --> 01:15:53.881
You become that glory that you are.

01:15:54.082 --> 01:15:56.821
And you rise into a new state

01:15:57.022 --> 01:16:02.220
that we call as of ‘collective consciousness’.

01:16:02.421 --> 01:16:07.702
This is the process of your evolution.

01:16:08.022 --> 01:16:11.702
And this is the last breakthrough of our evolution,

01:16:11.862 --> 01:16:16.462
where from human awareness you have to become

01:16:16.702 --> 01:16:21.222
a realized soul, a person who is born again.

01:16:21.422 --> 01:16:26.502
Like the birds are also called as ’dvijaha’ in Sanskrit language,

01:16:26.702 --> 01:16:28.902
meaning 'those who are born again';

01:16:29.102 --> 01:16:31.429
meaning, first they come as eggs

01:16:31.629 --> 01:16:34.329
and then they are born as birds. In the same way,

01:16:34.536 --> 01:16:36.421
it has to happen to you.

01:16:36.622 --> 01:16:38.907
And once these things happen,

01:16:39.098 --> 01:16:44.690
so many manifestations come through

01:16:44.891 --> 01:16:52.595
and we get the beautiful blessings of this All-Pervading Power.

01:16:53.262 --> 01:16:55.358
The first thing that happens to you,

01:16:55.556 --> 01:16:57.981
is that physically you feel fit.

01:16:58.182 --> 01:17:01.314
You feel fit with your own powers.

01:17:01.515 --> 01:17:03.941
No medicines are needed.

01:17:04.806 --> 01:17:07.759
No maneuvering is needed. Nothing is needed. You just,

01:17:07.960 --> 01:17:12.462
from your own power, which is lying in the triangular bone here.

01:17:12.662 --> 01:17:15.422
Have you talked to them something about it? No, it is not. Just...

01:17:15.662 --> 01:17:20.262
All right. In the triangular bone this Power lies

01:17:20.422 --> 01:17:23.302
which is called as Kundalini.

01:17:23.502 --> 01:17:26.262
I think it is too far away for them to see.

01:17:26.502 --> 01:17:30.982
Can it be brought, can we bring it forward?

01:17:31.182 --> 01:17:34.382
They can’t see it, so what's the use?

01:17:45.790 --> 01:17:48.550
Now all of you can see it?

01:17:49.821 --> 01:17:51.421
SY: This side. This side. Here.

01:17:51.622 --> 01:17:55.523
SM: It would be better? All right, this side.

01:17:55.770 --> 01:17:58.175
Can you see now?

01:18:00.103 --> 01:18:03.508
Just this way a little bit. These are all Sahaja Yogis, aren’t they?

01:18:03.709 --> 01:18:07.129
So, it is all right, for you need not see. You just put it this...

01:18:07.672 --> 01:18:10.145
Just little at an angle, please.

01:18:10.346 --> 01:18:13.782
Yes, now is better? All right.

01:18:14.022 --> 01:18:18.104
So, this subtle system exists within us.

01:18:18.305 --> 01:18:21.062
And we have to understand this subtle system.

01:18:21.262 --> 01:18:24.942
Like all our civilizations has grown outward, like a tree.

01:18:25.142 --> 01:18:29.822
And whatever we have knowledge through science or any other method,

01:18:30.022 --> 01:18:31.978
is the knowledge of the tree.

01:18:32.185 --> 01:18:34.581
But we have no knowledge of our roots.

01:18:34.782 --> 01:18:40.262
And that is why we are always under a threat of a shock

01:18:40.462 --> 01:18:42.956
and God knows what's going to happen to us.

01:18:43.157 --> 01:18:45.432
If we know our roots,

01:18:45.633 --> 01:18:49.262
then we know how to nourish this tree very well.

01:18:49.422 --> 01:18:53.862
Now here you see in the triangular bone, is this Power,

01:18:54.062 --> 01:18:56.465
what we call as Kundalini in a Sanskrit word,

01:18:56.666 --> 01:18:58.680
but ‘Kundal’ means coils,

01:18:58.863 --> 01:19:01.538
coiled up into three and a half coils.

01:19:01.739 --> 01:19:06.062
And this Power is the residual power within us

01:19:06.262 --> 01:19:10.942
which is waiting for that moment when it can be awakened.

01:19:11.143 --> 01:19:15.782
And like you have now connected by this cord to the mains,

01:19:15.942 --> 01:19:19.942
this Power rises and connects you to the mains.

01:19:20.142 --> 01:19:23.302
By that you become a subtler personality,

01:19:23.502 --> 01:19:26.462
you become that collective conscious personality,

01:19:26.662 --> 01:19:28.542
you go beyond thoughts.

01:19:28.718 --> 01:19:32.971
And as I told you, physically, mentally and emotionally

01:19:33.193 --> 01:19:37.526
you become absolutely a perfect personality.

01:19:37.727 --> 01:19:41.902
Apart from that, you achieve your peace of mind,

01:19:42.102 --> 01:19:44.519
all your tensions disappear

01:19:44.720 --> 01:19:48.341
and that you become a witness.

01:19:48.542 --> 01:19:53.662
Like a witness you see the play, the play of the Divine,

01:19:53.862 --> 01:19:59.662
and the complete knowledge of the Divine and the subtle knowledge,

01:19:59.862 --> 01:20:03.542
becomes your own; which is an absolute knowledge.

01:20:03.742 --> 01:20:08.462
Everybody who is in Sahaja Yoga knows the same thing.

01:20:08.702 --> 01:20:12.371
There is no argument, there is no fight,

01:20:12.562 --> 01:20:14.861
there is no discussion.

01:20:15.062 --> 01:20:17.782
Because once you get this Realization,

01:20:17.982 --> 01:20:20.749
when this Kundalini rises and passes through

01:20:20.932 --> 01:20:23.357
six subtle centers above,

01:20:23.558 --> 01:20:27.536
then you start feeling on your finger tips,

01:20:27.737 --> 01:20:30.566
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost, as they call it,

01:20:30.767 --> 01:20:34.157
or we can say the All Pervading Power.

01:20:34.411 --> 01:20:39.342
Also you can feel the cool breeze, out of your fontanel bone area

01:20:39.542 --> 01:20:41.822
when this Kundalini pierces through,

01:20:41.982 --> 01:20:47.382
and that is the actualization of baptism.

01:20:47.583 --> 01:20:48.999
Is not artificial

01:20:49.200 --> 01:20:52.111
that somebody puts the finger on your thing and say,

01:20:52.312 --> 01:20:53.718
"Now you are baptized."

01:20:53.919 --> 01:20:58.130
Baptism is a living process

01:20:58.331 --> 01:21:02.025
and it's a living process of evolution

01:21:02.200 --> 01:21:08.829
that gives you this new dimension to your awareness.

01:21:09.942 --> 01:21:14.582
Now the rising of the Kundalini is spontaneous

01:21:14.782 --> 01:21:18.382
because it's a living process. Like if you have a seed,

01:21:18.582 --> 01:21:23.782
it sprouts if you put it in the Mother Earth, spontaneously.

01:21:23.982 --> 01:21:26.049
We don’t have to stand [on] our heads

01:21:26.248 --> 01:21:29.372
or to read some sort of a book or a scripture.

01:21:29.573 --> 01:21:31.022
It just happens.

01:21:31.222 --> 01:21:33.937
In the same way, spontaneously,

01:21:34.138 --> 01:21:38.462
this power rises and connects you to the mains.

01:21:38.663 --> 01:21:41.262
As a result, as I told, you become dynamic,

01:21:41.462 --> 01:21:44.857
you become extremely creative,

01:21:45.058 --> 01:21:50.234
you feel very young, you work very hard, you don’t feel tired

01:21:50.435 --> 01:21:54.856
and so many diseases automatically get cured by your own power,

01:21:55.057 --> 01:21:56.358
by yourself.

01:21:56.559 --> 01:22:01.382
Nobody has to cure you. You just get absolutely cured out of it.

01:22:01.582 --> 01:22:07.713
For example, we have so many problems in the modern times,

01:22:07.914 --> 01:22:10.942
of very different nature:

01:22:11.142 --> 01:22:13.365
that people are overactive

01:22:13.548 --> 01:22:17.080
and over activity takes them away from reality

01:22:17.281 --> 01:22:21.103
and they become sort of slaves of over activity.

01:22:21.304 --> 01:22:26.761
This is done by the second center which is, you see, the yellow, the bile.

01:22:26.962 --> 01:22:29.262
This center is, for example,

01:22:29.422 --> 01:22:31.742
I will tell you about one center at least today,

01:22:31.942 --> 01:22:35.542
That this center is called as Swadisthana center

01:22:35.742 --> 01:22:39.862
and which looks after, on the physical side,

01:22:40.182 --> 01:22:43.622
and caters for aortic plexus.

01:22:43.822 --> 01:22:47.081
And this center has got a very important work to be done,

01:22:47.282 --> 01:22:53.497
is to convert the fat for the replacement

01:22:53.698 --> 01:22:56.929
of the grey cells of our brain.

01:22:57.130 --> 01:23:00.982
This is a very important work for people who are futuristic,

01:23:01.183 --> 01:23:04.302
who are planning all the time, who are thinking too much.

01:23:04.502 --> 01:23:09.462
As a result all other functions of this center are neglected.

01:23:09.662 --> 01:23:14.422
And these other functions are, that it has to cater to your liver.

01:23:14.622 --> 01:23:16.812
Now liver has a job,

01:23:16.980 --> 01:23:22.596
it has to transform the heat or the poison from your body,

01:23:22.797 --> 01:23:25.731
as heat into the blood stream

01:23:25.932 --> 01:23:29.022
so that it is thrown out.

01:23:29.222 --> 01:23:32.929
But when this center is busy

01:23:33.104 --> 01:23:35.821
doing something else, so important,

01:23:36.022 --> 01:23:40.982
this work is left undone or sometimes very much neglected.

01:23:41.182 --> 01:23:45.742
As a result one develops a bad system of liver.

01:23:45.942 --> 01:23:48.297
This liver creates heat,

01:23:48.481 --> 01:23:51.221
does not throw out the heat from the body

01:23:51.422 --> 01:23:55.975
which passes along and you get so many complications with it,

01:23:56.176 --> 01:23:59.605
like asthma and others.

01:24:00.742 --> 01:24:04.661
Today we had a patient who came and she had the same problem.

01:24:04.862 --> 01:24:08.553
And she said, "They have told me I have some viruses, this, that",

01:24:08.754 --> 01:24:10.902
all kinds of diagnosis she told Me.

01:24:11.102 --> 01:24:13.502
I said, "Nothing, you just have liver,

01:24:13.702 --> 01:24:17.298
and you just try to improve your liver, you will be all right".

01:24:17.499 --> 01:24:19.845
Within ten minutes she said, "I'm feeling all right".

01:24:20.036 --> 01:24:21.821
I said, "That's it.

01:24:22.022 --> 01:24:24.662
You have a liver problem. So this virus is there,

01:24:24.862 --> 01:24:28.542
that virus is there, all kinds of roundabout ways of saying

01:24:28.742 --> 01:24:32.462
to show that it is absolutely incurable".

01:24:32.662 --> 01:24:36.335
Now, then you go from there

01:24:36.536 --> 01:24:40.542
to another very important work, is that of the pancreas

01:24:40.742 --> 01:24:47.102
which looks after or caters of dissolving your sugar.

01:24:47.302 --> 01:24:51.662
But when you have this pancreas in a mess,

01:24:51.862 --> 01:24:56.382
because this center is not looking after it,

01:24:56.582 --> 01:24:59.982
then you develop a horrible disease called diabetes.

01:25:00.142 --> 01:25:02.342
And this diabetes only happens to people

01:25:02.543 --> 01:25:05.679
who sit down and think too much, who plan too much,

01:25:05.880 --> 01:25:08.342
mostly to bureaucrats,

01:25:08.582 --> 01:25:12.542
and maybe to politicians, I don’t know.

01:25:12.902 --> 01:25:16.982
But say in India, farmers ask for sugar

01:25:17.182 --> 01:25:22.102
and if you give them tea, the sugar should be so much

01:25:22.302 --> 01:25:25.782
that the spoon should stand at right angles, you see.

01:25:25.982 --> 01:25:30.142
Otherwise they'll think, "This is no tea, this is horrible!"

01:25:30.342 --> 01:25:34.860
And despite all that, they never get diabetes.

01:25:35.061 --> 01:25:38.822
But any bureaucrat who is too much of a planner

01:25:39.022 --> 01:25:42.806
or a politician or someone like that, who thinks too much,

01:25:44.139 --> 01:25:45.858
gets it even with one spoon,

01:25:46.059 --> 01:25:48.501
maybe with the half spoon he gets diabetes.

01:25:48.702 --> 01:25:52.957
So this is due to the fact that this poor center

01:25:53.158 --> 01:25:56.502
has to do some work for all these people

01:25:56.702 --> 01:25:59.622
who are extra active with their brains

01:25:59.822 --> 01:26:06.142
and other organs like pancreas, are neglected.

01:26:06.342 --> 01:26:10.782
Then third one is even more important, more dangerous is the spleen.

01:26:10.982 --> 01:26:13.902
The spleen is the one, which is, we can say,

01:26:14.102 --> 01:26:16.382
is the one which keeps the rhythm of life.

01:26:16.582 --> 01:26:20.382
As you have seen the rhythmic work, it keeps the rhythm of life.

01:26:20.582 --> 01:26:24.688
Now this rhythmic work,

01:26:24.889 --> 01:26:27.651
if we do not allow it to work with proper rhythm

01:26:27.858 --> 01:26:29.741
and we have become hectic,

01:26:29.942 --> 01:26:34.782
then this center has the job to create

01:26:34.982 --> 01:26:41.022
red blood corpuscles for the use of any emergencies.

01:26:41.222 --> 01:26:46.021
Supposing you have taken your food and suddenly you want to run,

01:26:46.222 --> 01:26:47.939
then you get a pain here

01:26:48.140 --> 01:26:50.201
and you don’t know why you are getting the pain.

01:26:50.402 --> 01:26:54.836
Because that time your spleen goes into action in a very frantic way

01:26:55.037 --> 01:26:58.673
and produces more RBCs, red blood corpuscles

01:26:58.874 --> 01:27:03.210
and with that, it has to work hard, you get that pain.

01:27:04.702 --> 01:27:09.247
Now when you lead such a hectic life, all the time under shocks,

01:27:09.448 --> 01:27:11.995
like early in the morning we read the newspapers;

01:27:12.146 --> 01:27:14.021
one shock is sufficient.

01:27:14.222 --> 01:27:17.860
Then secondly you have to have your breakfast,

01:27:18.061 --> 01:27:21.596
you can’t have time, you are in a busy, you are running away to work

01:27:21.797 --> 01:27:23.736
and on the way you find there is a jam.

01:27:23.937 --> 01:27:27.982
Then you go, your boss also shouting at you for getting late,

01:27:28.222 --> 01:27:30.822
all kinds of time bound things, you see.

01:27:30.982 --> 01:27:35.045
All these plays upon your spleen,

01:27:35.246 --> 01:27:37.156
and poor spleen doesn’t understand

01:27:37.357 --> 01:27:40.169
what sort of a personality is this one; is so hectic.

01:27:40.370 --> 01:27:44.041
God knows, it requires red blood corpuscles now and then

01:27:44.242 --> 01:27:47.462
and like that, is so hectic, there is no rhythm about it...

01:27:47.662 --> 01:27:50.982
so it gets, you should say, crazy.

01:27:51.222 --> 01:27:55.259
Then it becomes vulnerable, absolutely vulnerable

01:27:55.460 --> 01:27:58.720
for a disease called blood cancer.

01:27:59.662 --> 01:28:02.048
Then at the same time,

01:28:02.249 --> 01:28:06.382
if on the left side there is some triggering done, triggering

01:28:06.582 --> 01:28:09.542
due to some shock or some sort of pain or unhappiness

01:28:09.743 --> 01:28:11.620
or something like that,

01:28:11.827 --> 01:28:13.621
this disease sets in.

01:28:13.822 --> 01:28:17.722
Now people who have come to Sahaja Yoga, were certified

01:28:17.923 --> 01:28:20.902
to be dead within eight days also by doctors,

01:28:21.102 --> 01:28:22.902
who have suffered from this trouble,

01:28:23.102 --> 01:28:25.822
got themselves cured of blood cancer.

01:28:26.022 --> 01:28:28.419
Cancer is also cured with it, no doubt.

01:28:28.620 --> 01:28:31.918
But it is cured automatically by your own powers.

01:28:32.119 --> 01:28:35.862
Nobody has to cure you. You just get cured by your own powers.

01:28:36.062 --> 01:28:37.894
Once you get your Realization,

01:28:38.095 --> 01:28:40.404
and you know how to handle your own powers,

01:28:40.603 --> 01:28:41.964
how to treat yourself,

01:28:42.165 --> 01:28:44.942
first you can find out what is wrong with your centers,

01:28:45.102 --> 01:28:46.663
diagnosis is there,

01:28:46.838 --> 01:28:49.621
and you can find out also how to get it cured.

01:28:49.822 --> 01:28:51.283
You can cure yourself

01:28:51.484 --> 01:28:54.550
and you can help others to get their Realization.

01:28:54.751 --> 01:28:56.262
This is the power you get.

01:28:56.462 --> 01:28:59.141
It is not just a certificate, a false certificate,

01:28:59.342 --> 01:29:03.627
that, "I am a self-realized person, I am a twice-born person."

01:29:10.782 --> 01:29:15.702
It has to be a certificate from yourself

01:29:15.902 --> 01:29:17.942
that you have to feel the cool breeze.

01:29:18.142 --> 01:29:21.662
You have to feel that All Pervading Power.

01:29:21.862 --> 01:29:26.822
You have to feel your peace and your silence within yourself.

01:29:27.022 --> 01:29:29.382
So first of all when the Kundalini rises,

01:29:29.582 --> 01:29:32.228
She passes through this center

01:29:32.429 --> 01:29:34.221
which we call as Agnya,

01:29:34.422 --> 01:29:38.702
which is placed in the optic chasma.

01:29:38.902 --> 01:29:42.262
When this passes through that it sucks in from both the sides,

01:29:42.462 --> 01:29:44.822
these two institutions which are created

01:29:45.022 --> 01:29:48.222
by our left and right sympathetic nervous system.

01:29:48.422 --> 01:29:52.662
Whenever there is an emergency, the sympathetic goes into action.

01:29:52.862 --> 01:29:56.302
So here we have an autonomous nervous system.

01:29:56.502 --> 01:29:59.662
Autonomous nervous system is named by doctors.

01:29:59.862 --> 01:30:01.862
We have to ask them, "What do you mean by auto?

01:30:02.062 --> 01:30:04.182
Who is this 'auto'? Who does this job?"

01:30:04.382 --> 01:30:07.902
So we have left and right side of autonomous nervous system

01:30:08.102 --> 01:30:11.182
nourished by these two channels, left and right.

01:30:11.422 --> 01:30:14.622
And when this autonomous nervous system starts working

01:30:14.782 --> 01:30:17.491
either on the desire side

01:30:17.692 --> 01:30:20.220
or we can say emotional side, on the left hand side,

01:30:20.421 --> 01:30:24.501
it creates an institution here, which we call as superego,

01:30:24.702 --> 01:30:26.822
or in Sanskrit called as ‘Mana’,

01:30:27.022 --> 01:30:29.782
where all our conditionings are stored up.

01:30:29.982 --> 01:30:35.849
And on the other side, if the right side is too much excited,

01:30:36.050 --> 01:30:38.582
if a person is too much futuristic

01:30:38.782 --> 01:30:42.342
and is using too much his mental and physical capacities,

01:30:42.542 --> 01:30:44.267
then there is another institution

01:30:44.458 --> 01:30:46.437
that is created on top of your head,

01:30:46.638 --> 01:30:49.619
which we call as ‘ego’.

01:30:50.502 --> 01:30:53.582
These two meet and sometimes overlap

01:30:53.782 --> 01:30:56.982
and so we close our fontanel bone area

01:30:57.182 --> 01:31:00.467
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:31:01.222 --> 01:31:04.782
So when this Kundalini passes through this center

01:31:04.982 --> 01:31:07.016
which we call as Agnya Chakra,

01:31:07.217 --> 01:31:11.029
it sucks in these two institutions. So your karmas are sucked in

01:31:11.230 --> 01:31:14.142
and your conditionings are sucked in

01:31:14.343 --> 01:31:18.463
and it comes down like this, it opens this area,

01:31:18.662 --> 01:31:21.182
Kundalini pierces through this.

01:31:21.382 --> 01:31:24.062
Now this is a spontaneous thing happening.

01:31:24.262 --> 01:31:27.142
It is not that you have to do something about it.

01:31:27.342 --> 01:31:30.631
As the car starts, all the machinery starts working,

01:31:30.832 --> 01:31:33.329
this also starts working.

01:31:33.530 --> 01:31:36.222
But, in... say, "This is modern Raja yoga is there,

01:31:36.422 --> 01:31:39.862
Hatha yoga is there", everybody ask Me question after the lecture,

01:31:40.062 --> 01:31:42.542
so it is better I tell you about it already,

01:31:42.782 --> 01:31:45.490
that this so called Raja yoga is something

01:31:45.657 --> 01:31:49.885
like when the car has not yet started,

01:31:50.086 --> 01:31:51.942
the machinery won’t start.

01:31:52.142 --> 01:31:54.622
So without starting the car you start moving the wheels

01:31:54.822 --> 01:31:56.942
is the modern's Raja yoga.

01:31:57.142 --> 01:31:59.542
They even cut the tongues of, I mean

01:31:59.742 --> 01:32:03.302
not the tongues but the threads of the tongues of people,

01:32:03.502 --> 01:32:05.389
to push back the tongue,

01:32:05.627 --> 01:32:09.061
so that it can stop the Kundalini.

01:32:09.262 --> 01:32:13.942
But when the Kundalini is rising by itself, it stops.

01:32:14.142 --> 01:32:19.222
It stops every area it crosses through.

01:32:19.382 --> 01:32:23.342
Supposing it comes to this area, then when it passes through it,

01:32:23.542 --> 01:32:28.062
it has to go into an augmentation, into constriction

01:32:28.262 --> 01:32:30.862
to stop that Kundalini falling down.

01:32:31.062 --> 01:32:33.147
So it is done automatically.

01:32:33.322 --> 01:32:37.285
As we eat our food it gets digested, in the same way it happens.

01:32:37.486 --> 01:32:40.422
But artificially it is not to be done.

01:32:40.622 --> 01:32:44.062
And all these artificial doing is of no help.

01:32:44.262 --> 01:32:48.422
Same about Hatha yoga. Is ‘ha´-`tha’, is two words there,

01:32:48.622 --> 01:32:51.022
meaning the sun line and the moon line,

01:32:51.222 --> 01:32:54.342
meaning the left and the right side channel, both are to be used.

01:32:54.502 --> 01:32:57.342
But when we do Hatha yoga in the modern times,

01:32:57.582 --> 01:33:00.662
we are just trying to do only physical exercises

01:33:00.862 --> 01:33:04.149
which is a very wee, wee part of the Patanjali yoga,

01:33:04.350 --> 01:33:07.182
out of which Hatha yoga has come.

01:33:07.382 --> 01:33:09.982
In the Patanjali yoga is described that

01:33:10.182 --> 01:33:14.254
you have to see a person who has got problems on his physical side.

01:33:14.455 --> 01:33:17.758
Supposing now somebody has had an accident or something

01:33:17.959 --> 01:33:22.067
and the back bone is not all right and there is a problem on that.

01:33:22.268 --> 01:33:24.182
So you have to correct it.

01:33:24.382 --> 01:33:27.570
But this correction is the best once the Kundalini is up,

01:33:27.771 --> 01:33:29.422
so you know where is the problem

01:33:29.623 --> 01:33:31.862
and then is to be corrected scientifically.

01:33:32.062 --> 01:33:34.141
Not to be done in a haphazard manner.

01:33:34.342 --> 01:33:37.262
And sometimes the people do Hatha yoga in the way,

01:33:37.422 --> 01:33:41.662
that as if they are taking all the medicine boxes together,

01:33:41.863 --> 01:33:43.431
without any discrimination.

01:33:43.632 --> 01:33:45.747
So you should have discrimination about it

01:33:45.938 --> 01:33:48.101
and you should find out what’s wrong

01:33:48.302 --> 01:33:52.382
and then do exactly whatever is needed to be done.

01:33:52.583 --> 01:33:54.545
Not to do everything blindly.

01:33:54.746 --> 01:33:57.701
So the first thing, the blessings of Sahaja Yoga is

01:33:57.902 --> 01:34:00.142
that you get to know all the knowledge.

01:34:00.342 --> 01:34:02.222
It is not just you say this mantra,

01:34:02.422 --> 01:34:04.502
you do this thing, you do, nothing of that kind.

01:34:04.702 --> 01:34:08.022
You first become the Spirit.

01:34:08.262 --> 01:34:11.142
And you know everything about it, what it is.

01:34:11.342 --> 01:34:15.637
You experience it, you find out for yourself, you certify yourself

01:34:15.838 --> 01:34:19.182
and then you have to work it out.

01:34:19.422 --> 01:34:22.662
So it is a very practical, pragmatic thing.

01:34:22.822 --> 01:34:24.973
Of course you can’t pay for all these things.

01:34:25.174 --> 01:34:27.696
Those who are paying for this must know is a wrong thing,

01:34:27.846 --> 01:34:29.613
because it's a living process.

01:34:29.814 --> 01:34:32.662
For a living process how can you pay?

01:34:32.863 --> 01:34:35.280
It's something absurd but people don’t understand

01:34:35.434 --> 01:34:37.841
that you cannot pay for it

01:34:38.042 --> 01:34:39.635
because they don’t feel confident

01:34:39.836 --> 01:34:41.557
if you don’t have to pay for something.

01:34:41.758 --> 01:34:44.616
The other day I was in Cairns,

01:34:44.817 --> 01:34:46.986
and there is a Sahaja Yogini and she said, "Mother,

01:34:47.187 --> 01:34:51.086
they wouldn’t come to a program for which you don’t have to pay."

01:34:51.287 --> 01:34:53.302
"So then, what did you do?"

01:34:53.462 --> 01:34:56.462
She said, "I told them I will take 50 dollars from you."

01:34:56.702 --> 01:35:00.622
They all came with 50 dollars, quite happy and satisfied.

01:35:00.822 --> 01:35:02.750
So she took 50 dollars from them,

01:35:02.951 --> 01:35:05.588
gave them Realization, worked it out

01:35:05.789 --> 01:35:07.876
and then she returned the money saying,

01:35:08.077 --> 01:35:10.861
"I don’t need this money, sorry."

01:35:11.062 --> 01:35:13.862
But this kind of a psychology, I can’t understand

01:35:14.062 --> 01:35:17.503
that we are so much used to payment in everything

01:35:17.704 --> 01:35:20.542
that we cannot understand one thing, that

01:35:20.742 --> 01:35:23.259
Divine doesn’t know what is payment is.

01:35:23.460 --> 01:35:26.542
How much do we pay for this Mother Earth for sprouting everything,

01:35:26.742 --> 01:35:28.822
for giving us beautiful trees and things?

01:35:29.022 --> 01:35:32.182
How much did we do for Her that we have to pay for it?

01:35:32.342 --> 01:35:35.142
But this is something we don’t understand in the West.

01:35:35.382 --> 01:35:37.474
In India they do because they know

01:35:37.675 --> 01:35:41.043
that Divine has no sense of money.

01:35:41.244 --> 01:35:43.869
It doesn’t know banking, doesn’t know insurance,

01:35:44.070 --> 01:35:45.426
nothing of the kind.

01:35:45.627 --> 01:35:48.102
And this is what we have to understand first of all

01:35:48.302 --> 01:35:52.142
that if we have to become a divine personality,

01:35:52.382 --> 01:35:56.062
we must respect it as a pure thing.

01:35:56.262 --> 01:35:59.622
It doesn’t need any money, it doesn’t need anything.

01:35:59.862 --> 01:36:04.022
It just needs one thing which is the pure desire within you,

01:36:04.222 --> 01:36:07.022
because this is the power of pure desire,

01:36:07.222 --> 01:36:11.462
the desire that, "I have to become one with the Divine."

01:36:11.662 --> 01:36:13.827
All other desires are impure,

01:36:14.028 --> 01:36:18.502
because no desire when fulfilled, gives you satisfaction.

01:36:18.702 --> 01:36:21.942
You jump from one desire to another desire.

01:36:22.142 --> 01:36:26.022
That’s why it is said in economics that in general

01:36:26.182 --> 01:36:29.662
the desires and wants are not satiable.

01:36:29.862 --> 01:36:32.182
But this is the desire that we have.

01:36:32.382 --> 01:36:34.689
And once this desire is fulfilled,

01:36:34.890 --> 01:36:39.405
we become absolutely contented, satisfied

01:36:39.606 --> 01:36:43.542
and a complete balance is established within ourselves.

01:36:43.782 --> 01:36:46.902
All these ecological problems settle down

01:36:47.062 --> 01:36:51.334
because the imbalance in the human beings itself

01:36:51.535 --> 01:36:53.982
creates the imbalance outside.

01:36:54.182 --> 01:36:58.102
Whatever are human problems are projected outside.

01:36:58.302 --> 01:37:00.217
These are not problems

01:37:00.418 --> 01:37:03.302
which have come from nature, but are created by us.

01:37:03.502 --> 01:37:07.782
Because of our problems these problems arise.

01:37:07.982 --> 01:37:12.182
So somehow if we can manage to put ourself in proper line,

01:37:12.382 --> 01:37:18.541
everything will be fine and we will live in a new era of,

01:37:18.742 --> 01:37:20.858
what we call the Golden Age,

01:37:21.057 --> 01:37:23.781
and we enter into the Kingdom of God.

01:37:23.981 --> 01:37:26.581
Because then you will realize, yourself experience

01:37:26.782 --> 01:37:29.062
that every moment is so surprising,

01:37:29.262 --> 01:37:34.062
how it works out, how things just help you

01:37:34.222 --> 01:37:39.742
and how you manage to get over difficulties without any trouble!

01:37:39.942 --> 01:37:42.582
It is something so wonderful, so fantastic!

01:37:42.782 --> 01:37:45.542
And is sometimes people will be skeptical about it.

01:37:45.742 --> 01:37:47.582
They will think how can that be?

01:37:47.782 --> 01:37:50.138
But supposing there is a television set

01:37:50.339 --> 01:37:54.062
I take it to the ignorant people in our Indian villages

01:37:54.222 --> 01:37:55.610
and show them and say that

01:37:55.811 --> 01:37:57.681
"You can see all kinds of films in this one",

01:37:57.882 --> 01:38:00.273
They will say, "What, this box! How can it show?"

01:38:00.474 --> 01:38:02.375
So we treat ourselves as that box.

01:38:02.576 --> 01:38:04.346
But actually when you put it to the mains,

01:38:04.512 --> 01:38:06.381
you know how fantastic it is.

01:38:06.582 --> 01:38:09.182
So, we are not created just for nothing.

01:38:09.342 --> 01:38:11.083
We are created for a special work,

01:38:11.284 --> 01:38:13.642
only thing is we have to know our Self.

01:38:13.843 --> 01:38:18.022
And all the scriptures and religions have said ‘know thy self’.

01:38:18.182 --> 01:38:22.633
But all of them have gone astray, absolutely astray,

01:38:22.834 --> 01:38:25.822
they have become all man-made sort of things.

01:38:26.022 --> 01:38:31.488
And that is why people are in complete disillusionment about them.

01:38:31.689 --> 01:38:34.622
But whosoever created them,

01:38:34.782 --> 01:38:37.862
all those great prophets, incarnations

01:38:38.062 --> 01:38:42.751
are absolutely truthful people and they told the truth.

01:38:42.952 --> 01:38:45.544
All the saints were truthful people.

01:38:45.745 --> 01:38:47.507
And we have to learn from them

01:38:47.708 --> 01:38:50.102
and we ourselves have to become saints.

01:38:50.302 --> 01:38:52.045
We don’t have to give up our families,

01:38:52.246 --> 01:38:55.114
we don’t have to do all this nonsensical things which are outside.

01:38:55.315 --> 01:38:57.462
The detachment works out within yourself.

01:38:57.702 --> 01:38:59.782
Everything works out within yourself

01:38:59.983 --> 01:39:02.282
and I am sure today, in Brisbane,

01:39:02.473 --> 01:39:04.581
we'll be achieving it for all of you.

01:39:04.782 --> 01:39:09.902
Because modern Sahaja Yoga is an en masse happening.

01:39:10.102 --> 01:39:13.211
Formerly, only one or two people used to get Realization;

01:39:13.412 --> 01:39:16.942
on the tree of life there were only one or two flowers.

01:39:17.142 --> 01:39:18.971
But today I call it a blossom time.

01:39:19.172 --> 01:39:22.565
And also this is the Day of Judgment,

01:39:22.733 --> 01:39:24.381
where we judge ourselves.

01:39:24.582 --> 01:39:27.462
In the Koran it is said that your hands would speak

01:39:27.662 --> 01:39:29.582
and you will judge yourself.

01:39:29.783 --> 01:39:33.005
But even the Muslims are not following what He said,

01:39:33.206 --> 01:39:35.946
even the Christians are not following what Christ has said,

01:39:36.147 --> 01:39:39.330
even the Hindus are not following what their Scriptures have said.

01:39:39.531 --> 01:39:41.640
They are all having a nice

01:39:41.841 --> 01:39:46.262
money-oriented or power-oriented organization.

01:39:46.462 --> 01:39:48.088
That is not going to help us.

01:39:48.287 --> 01:39:51.141
We have to have the Reality, the Truth.

01:39:51.342 --> 01:39:53.827
It is for our benevolence,

01:39:54.002 --> 01:39:56.061
for the benevolence of our children,

01:39:56.262 --> 01:39:58.422
for the benevolence of the whole world.

01:39:58.622 --> 01:40:01.622
That is how the whole humanity has to emancipate.

01:40:01.822 --> 01:40:05.222
And that's what I am here to tell you about.

01:40:05.382 --> 01:40:07.902
May God bless you all!

01:40:11.382 --> 01:40:15.897
We are rather time bound because they told Me

01:40:16.098 --> 01:40:19.502
that your conveyance is a problem here

01:40:19.702 --> 01:40:23.582
and that I should finish everything before 9.30.

01:40:23.782 --> 01:40:28.702
So I have to tell you one thing that if you could

01:40:28.903 --> 01:40:31.618
ask Me some questions that you have, relevant questions,

01:40:31.819 --> 01:40:34.134
because I am not here to take anything from you.

01:40:34.335 --> 01:40:36.462
I am here just to tell you what you are

01:40:36.662 --> 01:40:39.022
and to see that you get what you have.

01:40:39.182 --> 01:40:41.332
So if you have any relevant questions,

01:40:41.523 --> 01:40:44.932
please ask Me for a few minutes.

01:40:45.133 --> 01:40:48.148
And then we will have the session for Realization

01:40:48.349 --> 01:40:50.108
that will take about ten minutes.

01:40:50.309 --> 01:40:54.382
So I'll be very happy if you could ask Me questions about it.

01:40:54.582 --> 01:40:57.919
One thing I have to say and excuse Myself

01:40:58.120 --> 01:41:01.327
that in a one-day lecture,

01:41:01.528 --> 01:41:03.437
I cannot cover the whole subject.

01:41:03.638 --> 01:41:06.101
It is an ocean of knowledge.

01:41:06.302 --> 01:41:09.302
And this ocean of knowledge can be understood better

01:41:09.502 --> 01:41:11.230
when you have Self Realization,

01:41:11.374 --> 01:41:14.418
the light of your Spirit in your attention.

01:41:14.619 --> 01:41:17.462
You will understand it much better.

01:41:17.662 --> 01:41:20.622
But there are My lectures, so many, thousands of them

01:41:20.804 --> 01:41:22.413
in English language itself.

01:41:22.614 --> 01:41:24.542
So you can listen to them also.

01:41:24.742 --> 01:41:28.622
But first, the best thing is to get your Realization.

01:41:28.822 --> 01:41:31.062
For example there are so many lights here

01:41:31.262 --> 01:41:32.728
and when you come in

01:41:32.903 --> 01:41:36.285
what you do is to just switch on and the whole thing comes up.

01:41:36.486 --> 01:41:40.222
But supposing I have tell you everything about the electricity,

01:41:40.422 --> 01:41:43.542
the discovery of electricity, then how it was brought here,

01:41:43.742 --> 01:41:46.702
and in Brisbane how it was arranged, it will be a headache.

01:41:46.902 --> 01:41:48.471
So best is to get the lights

01:41:48.672 --> 01:41:52.462
and then we'lll know more about the knowledge of it.

01:41:52.662 --> 01:41:54.502
May God bless you!

01:42:03.420 --> 01:42:06.822
M: I would like to know how to perform meditation.

01:42:09.349 --> 01:42:11.763
SY: He'd like to know how to perform meditation.

01:42:11.964 --> 01:42:14.581
SM: It's good question. That is what I am going to do now.

01:42:14.782 --> 01:42:17.072
You do not do meditation

01:42:17.279 --> 01:42:20.061
but you are in meditation.

01:42:20.262 --> 01:42:23.542
It is a state. It is a state in which you rise,

01:42:23.742 --> 01:42:26.502
where you become thoughtlessly aware to begin with.

01:42:26.702 --> 01:42:28.982
You are aware but there is no thought.

01:42:29.182 --> 01:42:31.302
And whenever you want to think, you will think,

01:42:31.502 --> 01:42:33.942
otherwise you can stop your thoughts. That is first state.

01:42:34.142 --> 01:42:37.982
And the second one is called as doubtless awareness

01:42:38.182 --> 01:42:40.502
where you have no doubts left about it

01:42:40.702 --> 01:42:43.168
and you just become so powerful

01:42:43.369 --> 01:42:45.496
that you can give Realizations to others,

01:42:45.697 --> 01:42:49.662
you can do so many things, which normally you could have never done.

01:42:49.862 --> 01:42:52.302
These two states are to be achieved.

01:42:52.502 --> 01:42:55.222
So we don’t have to do meditation as such,

01:42:55.422 --> 01:42:59.862
it just will work out. You will be in meditation.

01:43:01.397 --> 01:43:04.622
L: Can you put it [louder]? I am not hearing You...

01:43:04.823 --> 01:43:07.249
SY: Not hearing very well?
L: No, I am not.

01:43:07.450 --> 01:43:10.699
SY: Do you hear [unclear]?

01:43:12.014 --> 01:43:14.307
SM: What is it?

01:43:15.381 --> 01:43:16.597
What is it?

01:43:16.820 --> 01:43:20.821
SY: The speakers, there is a noise in the speakers and I want to see...

01:43:21.022 --> 01:43:25.582
SM: There is a noise on? Some sort of a noise ...

01:43:25.902 --> 01:43:30.062
Next time we will have better arrangements for you.

01:43:30.632 --> 01:43:32.653
But whatever may be the problem,

01:43:32.844 --> 01:43:36.415
you will get your Realizations all right.

01:43:43.029 --> 01:43:45.582
What is it?

01:43:46.452 --> 01:43:49.021
SY: She wants me to give you another mike or something.

01:43:49.222 --> 01:43:50.942
Is not good?

01:44:00.282 --> 01:44:05.368
SY: She wants to know, does reincarnation affect individual spirits?

01:44:05.904 --> 01:44:08.406
SM: Individual spirits?

01:44:10.742 --> 01:44:13.307
I didn't...
SY: That is the question. Could you...?

01:44:13.508 --> 01:44:15.914
L: You know, about rebirth, do we all reincarnate?

01:44:16.113 --> 01:44:17.941
Do we all have another life?

01:44:18.142 --> 01:44:19.662
SY: Do we all reincarnate?

01:44:19.862 --> 01:44:22.694
SM: Of course. No doubt.

01:44:23.393 --> 01:44:26.701
You see you must logically understand.

01:44:26.902 --> 01:44:31.822
Now supposing you were in a certain century

01:44:32.342 --> 01:44:36.022
and you had committed some mistakes, supposing,

01:44:36.222 --> 01:44:38.889
or you have done something good,

01:44:39.072 --> 01:44:42.221
or you were searching something,

01:44:42.422 --> 01:44:44.865
you were wanting something.

01:44:45.056 --> 01:44:47.181
Then, I mean,

01:44:47.382 --> 01:44:52.022
you are not going to be condemned by one life, isn’t it?

01:44:52.261 --> 01:44:57.501
Because God Almighty is the ocean of forgiveness

01:44:57.702 --> 01:44:59.071
and He loves you

01:44:59.272 --> 01:45:01.941
and He wants you to enter into the Kingdom of God.

01:45:02.142 --> 01:45:04.569
So He gives you more chances.

01:45:04.752 --> 01:45:08.911
I will tell you one thing that we had a driver

01:45:09.112 --> 01:45:12.756
and he was a very quiet and very stately personality.

01:45:14.096 --> 01:45:21.173
And he told Me that he has become a driver

01:45:21.382 --> 01:45:25.422
because in last life he must have been some king

01:45:25.622 --> 01:45:29.502
and the king must have been over burdened with work.

01:45:29.702 --> 01:45:33.302
So the king must have thought is better to be a driver

01:45:33.502 --> 01:45:35.773
and there is no burdening of this,

01:45:35.974 --> 01:45:40.142
"So, I have become a driver and very happy about it".

01:45:40.302 --> 01:45:42.622
In the same way, you see, things can happen

01:45:42.862 --> 01:45:44.662
that you are searching for something.

01:45:44.863 --> 01:45:46.863
Like somebody wants to marry some lady.

01:45:46.982 --> 01:45:48.945
I mean is just mad

01:45:49.121 --> 01:45:51.617
and he suffers from Greek tragedy you can call it,

01:45:51.818 --> 01:45:54.262
and goes into a kind of a nonsensical ideas,

01:45:54.462 --> 01:45:59.308
doesn’t love his wife and just thinks of another woman all the time,

01:45:59.509 --> 01:46:01.942
and thinks that, "I should get married to her".

01:46:02.142 --> 01:46:06.182
So the next life, the Divine says, "All right, have her!"

01:46:06.382 --> 01:46:10.550
And then he says, "Oh, God! What a wife! Better run away."

01:46:10.751 --> 01:46:12.218
So he learns a lesson.

01:46:12.419 --> 01:46:15.821
So it is like giving lessons in your different lives.

01:46:16.022 --> 01:46:17.747
Is very important

01:46:17.948 --> 01:46:20.603
because God is not going to just damn you like that,

01:46:20.762 --> 01:46:24.101
that you are good for nothing, is not going to stamp you like that.

01:46:24.302 --> 01:46:25.750
Is a wrong idea.

01:46:25.933 --> 01:46:28.684
And because Christ also has said, "I will come again".

01:46:28.885 --> 01:46:33.694
If He had not believed in reincarnation why did He say that?

01:46:34.488 --> 01:46:36.862
Very irrelevant.

01:46:46.022 --> 01:46:50.422
It has, you see in the, between the lines you must be able to read.

01:46:50.622 --> 01:46:54.317
And that is the problem is that, between the lines we cannot read

01:46:54.518 --> 01:46:56.223
because we are not realized souls.

01:46:56.424 --> 01:46:58.546
Once we are realized souls

01:46:58.697 --> 01:47:01.297
we start seeing everything between the lines.

01:47:01.498 --> 01:47:03.182
Otherwise we cannot understand.

01:47:03.383 --> 01:47:05.763
And the whole thing becomes superficial

01:47:05.963 --> 01:47:09.476
and people who are interested only in money building and all that

01:47:09.677 --> 01:47:11.622
start some sort of a wrong idea

01:47:11.822 --> 01:47:15.875
and we get absolutely deluded by them.

01:47:28.022 --> 01:47:33.856
M: What is the place of Christ in them? What is [the relation]?

01:47:34.142 --> 01:47:35.866
SM: What is the...?

01:47:36.067 --> 01:47:39.622
SY: He said where is Christ in this set up and what is the relation?

01:47:39.862 --> 01:47:44.421
SM: On the Agnya, on the Agnya chakra.
M: But what is the relation?

01:47:44.622 --> 01:47:47.262
SM: You see because He is on the optic chiasma

01:47:47.461 --> 01:47:50.431
which we, sometimes people call it "a third eye".

01:47:50.632 --> 01:47:52.169
He is on the Agnya chakra.

01:47:52.370 --> 01:47:56.159
Now what I am saying is - you can verify it on your vibrations -

01:47:56.360 --> 01:47:58.131
because when the Kundalini rises

01:47:58.314 --> 01:48:00.440
and She comes up to the Agnya chakra,

01:48:00.641 --> 01:48:02.942
you have to say Lord’s prayer.

01:48:03.102 --> 01:48:07.686
And that’s how He has died for our sins.

01:48:07.887 --> 01:48:11.382
He has died for our sins means, He, once He is awakened,

01:48:11.622 --> 01:48:16.182
that all our conditionings and all our ego is sucked in.

01:48:16.342 --> 01:48:20.942
He is a very, very important gate through which we have to pass.

01:48:21.182 --> 01:48:22.540
He said “I am the gate”.

01:48:22.741 --> 01:48:26.018
He didn’t say, "I am the destination", but "I am the gate".

01:48:26.219 --> 01:48:27.541
Very clear.

01:48:27.742 --> 01:48:29.376
Christ's life you cannot understand

01:48:29.577 --> 01:48:32.120
unless and until you have your Realization. Not at all.

01:48:32.321 --> 01:48:35.422
Through these priests and all that, you cannot understand it at all.

01:48:35.622 --> 01:48:39.822
Specially, Mr. Paul, I don’t know how he appeared in the scene,

01:48:39.982 --> 01:48:42.194
because he himself was epileptic

01:48:42.395 --> 01:48:45.536
and some sort of an experience he had,

01:48:45.737 --> 01:48:48.784
and this spoiling Christianity has
been criticized by so many people.

01:48:48.985 --> 01:48:54.042
Recently I read a book written by a very good German priest

01:48:54.243 --> 01:48:55.941
when Christ was in India,

01:48:56.142 --> 01:49:00.142
and he has absolutely condemned Paul in Christianity;

01:49:00.342 --> 01:49:02.822
he said he has brought all kinds of things

01:49:03.022 --> 01:49:05.648
which are not relevant to Christ.

01:49:05.839 --> 01:49:09.902
Then also there was a book written by Thomas

01:49:10.103 --> 01:49:12.062
who was travelling to India

01:49:12.262 --> 01:49:14.554
and on his way he stopped in Egypt

01:49:14.755 --> 01:49:17.046
where he wrote lot of treatises

01:49:17.247 --> 01:49:20.529
and also wrote about what Christ had said it

01:49:20.704 --> 01:49:22.981
and was kept in a big jar.

01:49:23.182 --> 01:49:27.102
And he called all these people who followed Christ, as ‘gnostics’.

01:49:27.302 --> 01:49:29.151
Gnostics - those who know, ‘Gna’.

01:49:29.352 --> 01:49:31.399
‘Gna’ word comes from the word ‘jnana’.

01:49:31.600 --> 01:49:34.382
‘Jnana’ means to know on your central nervous system.

01:49:34.582 --> 01:49:38.542
Is also in Buddhist thing, is called as ‘ Boddha’.

01:49:38.742 --> 01:49:42.062
‘Buddh’, ‘ Boddha’ is to know on your central nervous system.

01:49:42.262 --> 01:49:48.182
And also, say in the Hindu scriptures is called as ‘vida’

01:49:48.382 --> 01:49:50.293
means from where the word ‘Veda’ comes,

01:49:50.494 --> 01:49:53.342
that you have to know on your central nervous system.

01:49:53.582 --> 01:49:57.582
Now, this book has been now after 48 years,

01:49:57.782 --> 01:50:00.262
it has been now decoded and found out and

01:50:00.462 --> 01:50:02.862
there was a very nice program on this.

01:50:03.102 --> 01:50:07.822
And it was all challenging, all these ideas of Paul in Christianity.

01:50:08.022 --> 01:50:11.382
You don’t have to suffer. He said, "Why should you suffer?",

01:50:11.582 --> 01:50:15.142
because God Almighty is the Father of all the fathers,

01:50:15.342 --> 01:50:17.422
and why should we ask you to suffer?

01:50:17.582 --> 01:50:19.402
Christ has already suffered for you.

01:50:19.603 --> 01:50:21.341
Now, you are not going to suffer more.

01:50:21.542 --> 01:50:24.462
So many things like that and also about Sahaja Yoga,

01:50:24.662 --> 01:50:28.262
that it’s a spontaneous experience which must be experienced

01:50:28.462 --> 01:50:31.982
and must be felt on the central nervous system.

01:50:32.222 --> 01:50:35.822
He said so clearly, on your nerves, as he said it.

01:50:36.022 --> 01:50:39.119
So, this book has been written down

01:50:39.320 --> 01:50:40.997
and is known as "The Gnostics".

01:50:41.198 --> 01:50:43.382
If you can get hold of it, please go through it.

01:50:43.582 --> 01:50:46.440
It’s a wonderful book which will give you full idea

01:50:46.592 --> 01:50:48.477
as to what Thomas wrote about.

01:50:48.678 --> 01:50:50.942
And these people were called as ‘Gnostics’.

01:50:51.142 --> 01:50:52.900
They were not called as Christians,

01:50:53.101 --> 01:50:55.462
but ‘Gnostics’ means the ones who have known.

01:50:55.662 --> 01:50:57.990
Known what? Known, not through your brains,

01:50:58.191 --> 01:51:00.501
but known on your central nervous system.

01:51:00.702 --> 01:51:04.713
As in Sanskrit language is called as ’Gynanis’.

01:51:10.599 --> 01:51:14.255
M: Could You tell us a bit more about the rising of the Kundalini,

01:51:14.456 --> 01:51:17.851
when this Kundalini rise, can we make Kundalini rise?

01:51:18.052 --> 01:51:21.085
Is it dangerous [unclear]?

01:51:22.128 --> 01:51:26.581
SY: Could You tell us some more about Kundalini. Is it dangerous to rise?

01:51:26.782 --> 01:51:29.942
SM: No, not at all. This [part], I should have covered Myself.

01:51:30.142 --> 01:51:33.142
Not at all, is never dangerous, you see.

01:51:33.342 --> 01:51:36.902
It’s your Mother. She is your individual Mother.

01:51:37.102 --> 01:51:41.102
When you were born your mother took all the labor pains upon herself.

01:51:41.302 --> 01:51:43.135
She didn’t give you any pain.

01:51:43.302 --> 01:51:45.941
In the same way She is your Mother

01:51:46.142 --> 01:51:49.072
and that’s a Mother energy, that is the primordial Mother

01:51:49.273 --> 01:51:50.781
which is reflected in you.

01:51:50.982 --> 01:51:53.422
That’s the Holy Ghost. They didn’t talk of Mother

01:51:53.623 --> 01:51:55.141
but they said it is a dove.

01:51:55.342 --> 01:51:56.869
I don’t know why they said it,

01:51:57.070 --> 01:51:59.141
but this is the Primordial Mother, no doubt.

01:51:59.342 --> 01:52:02.788
Because you have the God, the Father,

01:52:02.971 --> 01:52:04.127
God the Son,

01:52:04.328 --> 01:52:06.054
and what about the Mother?

01:52:06.229 --> 01:52:08.586
That's the Holy Ghost. It is a mystery.

01:52:08.787 --> 01:52:10.357
It's no mystery for us.

01:52:10.558 --> 01:52:13.182
You will know that the Holy Ghost is nothing else

01:52:13.382 --> 01:52:16.724
but the Primordial Mother called as ‘Adi Shakti’

01:52:16.902 --> 01:52:18.319
and by so many names.

01:52:18.520 --> 01:52:20.822
Like here is the river, is called as ‘Parramatta’,

01:52:20.982 --> 01:52:24.542
is the Primordial Mother. Is a absolutely a Sanskrit word.

01:52:24.742 --> 01:52:27.365
`Parramatta´ is absolutely Sanskrit word

01:52:27.566 --> 01:52:29.868
saying Primordial Mother [Param Mata].

01:52:30.662 --> 01:52:36.062
So this Mother is not going to give any trouble to you whatsoever.

01:52:36.262 --> 01:52:39.422
And those who say so, because they do not know how to do it,

01:52:39.622 --> 01:52:43.729
they want to frighten you and keep you away from reality.

01:52:44.742 --> 01:52:47.222
They have no authority. If they had divine authority,

01:52:47.422 --> 01:52:50.219
if they had some ways and methods of saying so,

01:52:50.420 --> 01:52:51.925
they would have said so.

01:52:52.113 --> 01:52:54.782
Like many people also say that the time has also not come.

01:52:54.983 --> 01:52:57.822
Because they don’t know how to do it.

01:52:58.262 --> 01:53:02.478
That’s why they are postponing it. It is very selfish, I should say,

01:53:02.679 --> 01:53:07.341
or all self-opiniatedness that to say that this is so and this is so.

01:53:07.542 --> 01:53:10.622
The Kundalini of course will never trouble you.

01:53:10.822 --> 01:53:12.894
But if you try wrong methods

01:53:13.061 --> 01:53:15.272
then naturally there is a heat in the body

01:53:15.473 --> 01:53:17.462
and the deities get angry with you,

01:53:17.622 --> 01:53:21.154
the innocence gets angry and tortures you.

01:53:22.502 --> 01:53:24.702
These false gurus who have come all over,

01:53:24.902 --> 01:53:27.181
I am ashamed of them and they are the ones

01:53:27.382 --> 01:53:29.519
who have mesmerized and taken money from you.

01:53:29.720 --> 01:53:31.622
I mean how can they take money from you

01:53:31.822 --> 01:53:34.103
and how can they be your gurus when they are taking

01:53:34.304 --> 01:53:37.444
all this kind of money from you? Just think of it.

01:53:37.645 --> 01:53:39.547
They are just you have retained them,

01:53:39.748 --> 01:53:41.702
they are like your servants I should say.

01:53:41.903 --> 01:53:44.182
They have no self respect.

01:53:47.298 --> 01:53:49.342
All right, you can pay for this hall all right.

01:53:49.542 --> 01:53:53.182
But you can’t pay for your Self Realization.

01:54:03.113 --> 01:54:09.389
L: Do You teach a system of [unclear] the chakras

01:54:09.558 --> 01:54:14.017
is necessary and do You describe [unclear].

01:54:15.662 --> 01:54:18.902
SY: Do You teach a method of cleansing the chakras?

01:54:19.141 --> 01:54:24.341
SM: Of course, of course.
L: [unclear] SM: Of course.

01:54:24.542 --> 01:54:26.736
We have a very good center here

01:54:26.937 --> 01:54:29.658
and we have very capable Sahaja Yogis,

01:54:29.817 --> 01:54:34.270
those who know how to cleanse your own chakras and everything.

01:54:34.471 --> 01:54:37.990
Of course, that's the minimum.

01:54:38.839 --> 01:54:41.742
And you yourself will be equipped with it.

01:54:41.942 --> 01:54:45.204
You yourself will know all these things.

01:54:46.102 --> 01:54:49.942
All that will be done. Is not just this lecture.

01:54:50.143 --> 01:54:53.102
There is a follow on. Please, all of you should come.

01:54:53.302 --> 01:54:55.822
It is not only Me, they also know everything

01:54:56.022 --> 01:54:59.101
and you will also know everything. That’s how it is going to spread.

01:54:59.302 --> 01:55:01.982
Like one enlightened light enlightens another

01:55:02.142 --> 01:55:05.902
and then that enlightened light enlightens another person.

01:55:06.102 --> 01:55:09.262
They are very very equipped here. They know everything about it.

01:55:09.462 --> 01:55:11.262
They have My lectures and things also.

01:55:11.502 --> 01:55:13.222
The main thing is they know everything

01:55:13.382 --> 01:55:16.653
and you have to know everything yourself.

01:55:21.585 --> 01:55:26.045
L: May I just ask You, humans don't carry the burden of original sin?

01:55:28.462 --> 01:55:31.302
SY: Do we still carry the burden of original sin?

01:55:31.502 --> 01:55:35.102
SM: No, not at all. It’s over now. Time is over.

01:55:35.302 --> 01:55:37.902
The original sin only brought us to ignorance

01:55:38.102 --> 01:55:40.062
and we started searching ourselves.

01:55:40.262 --> 01:55:41.982
Otherwise things would have been much better

01:55:42.182 --> 01:55:43.698
if we had not gone into it.

01:55:43.899 --> 01:55:45.470
But whatever it is, is now

01:55:45.622 --> 01:55:48.821
you had to come through a very circuitous way to understand.

01:55:49.022 --> 01:55:53.398
Because human beings, you see, as they were at that time, also

01:55:53.599 --> 01:55:55.702
wanted to find out about themselves.

01:55:55.942 --> 01:55:59.222
So God said, "All right, you have this freedom."

01:55:59.382 --> 01:56:02.182
Only human beings have the freedom, not the animals.

01:56:02.382 --> 01:56:04.779
Animals are called as ‘Pashu’ means they are under bond,

01:56:04.954 --> 01:56:06.803
they are under the bondage of God,

01:56:07.004 --> 01:56:10.182
and is already all controlled by Him.

01:56:10.382 --> 01:56:13.942
For example a scorpion is a scorpion, snake is a snake,

01:56:14.142 --> 01:56:17.622
they keep to their own dharma, means their own valences,

01:56:17.862 --> 01:56:19.822
their own religion, we can call it.

01:56:19.982 --> 01:56:22.862
They don’t change. But human beings can be a scorpion,

01:56:23.062 --> 01:56:26.742
can be lion, can be tiger, can be anything.

01:56:27.502 --> 01:56:30.102
They just shoot out like Jack in the box, you know.

01:56:30.302 --> 01:56:32.160
Sometimes you don’t know what’s the matter

01:56:32.361 --> 01:56:34.585
now suddenly from where it is coming?

01:56:34.807 --> 01:56:36.483
Is interesting, isn’t it?

01:56:36.684 --> 01:56:39.302
But then once you are realized you see it as drama,

01:56:39.502 --> 01:56:42.901
and you just see that whole thing is just working out

01:56:43.102 --> 01:56:44.839
in a very funny manner.

01:56:45.030 --> 01:56:47.765
You don’t take it so seriously as we normally do.

01:56:47.966 --> 01:56:49.982
And you just enjoy everything.

01:56:50.182 --> 01:56:52.981
And by your own countenance, by your own temperament,

01:56:53.182 --> 01:56:56.062
by your own character, people change.

01:56:56.262 --> 01:56:58.702
And they ask, "How are you like this?"

01:56:58.902 --> 01:57:01.902
Then you say that "We have become Sahaja Yogis,

01:57:02.102 --> 01:57:04.982
so they come to you and they become Sahaja Yogis, too.

01:57:05.182 --> 01:57:07.902
It's a wonderful area, it's a wonderful time

01:57:08.102 --> 01:57:10.662
and such wonderful people all over the world.

01:57:10.862 --> 01:57:14.136
Like I went to USSR, you will be surprised, USSR.

01:57:14.337 --> 01:57:18.782
And I never expected, they never have heard of any God or anything,

01:57:18.982 --> 01:57:22.102
and Christ also, they were just keeping Him aloof.

01:57:22.302 --> 01:57:24.096
And there it is the people,

01:57:24.247 --> 01:57:26.560
thousands they came and they got Realization,

01:57:26.751 --> 01:57:28.455
settled down into them, very deep people.

01:57:28.656 --> 01:57:31.990
They touched their depth. I was amazed. But the best part of it,

01:57:32.191 --> 01:57:34.822
that the Germans went to give them Realization.

01:57:35.022 --> 01:57:40.623
25 Germans rushed there, to help Me out. I was amazed, you see.

01:57:40.824 --> 01:57:43.560
And I said, "It must have cost you" , but they said, "Mother,

01:57:43.761 --> 01:57:46.432
what is the money for? We have to come for Russians".

01:57:46.633 --> 01:57:49.942
And such love and such understanding, you see.

01:57:50.142 --> 01:57:52.262
I was really touched by their beauty.

01:57:52.462 --> 01:57:57.257
Can you imagine Germans giving Realization to Russians?

01:57:58.342 --> 01:58:03.504
So beautiful it is to see their beauty expressing itself.

01:58:06.972 --> 01:58:10.487
Yes.
SY: One raised at the back.

01:58:10.931 --> 01:58:14.259
M: [unclear].

01:58:14.460 --> 01:58:18.467
How it will, what it represents [unclear]?

01:58:18.665 --> 01:58:20.656
How is it the divine state?

01:58:20.792 --> 01:58:24.783
And [unclear] what is guiding us now?

01:58:25.116 --> 01:58:28.245
And is it possible that some people have

01:58:28.452 --> 01:58:31.701
without particular effort [unclear].

01:58:31.902 --> 01:58:34.228
SM: What is he saying?

01:58:58.810 --> 01:59:00.422
What is he talking?

01:59:00.622 --> 01:59:03.569
M: Mother, if rising Kundalini is what [unclear] ,

01:59:03.760 --> 01:59:06.527
how would You describe the current state?

01:59:06.728 --> 01:59:09.430
And what is it that is driving us now?

01:59:10.142 --> 01:59:11.438
SM: Driving you?

01:59:11.639 --> 01:59:14.385
SY: No, he said Kundalini is the [unclear] thing.

01:59:14.562 --> 01:59:18.875
Then Kundalini rises and that's how we wake up all of them,

01:59:19.076 --> 01:59:21.034
and that Realization [rises], Mother.

01:59:21.241 --> 01:59:23.905
What is the current state and what about the state are we [now]?

01:59:24.106 --> 01:59:28.662
SM: No, you are at a state which we call as human awareness at its best.

01:59:28.862 --> 01:59:32.942
When you start thinking "Why am I here on this earth?",

01:59:33.142 --> 01:59:37.742
you are trying to find out, because you see many things

01:59:37.942 --> 01:59:41.182
which do not satisfy you and you think this is not absolute.

01:59:41.382 --> 01:59:44.062
Why there are so many opinions about everything?

01:59:44.262 --> 01:59:46.496
Why people think differently?

01:59:46.647 --> 01:59:48.628
And all these things come to your mind.

01:59:48.829 --> 01:59:52.262
then you become what we call as a seeker of truth.

01:59:52.463 --> 01:59:56.622
Is that is the state, is ‘Sadaka’ and that seeking brings you here.

01:59:56.822 --> 01:59:58.703
And then you get your Realization.

01:59:58.904 --> 02:00:01.865
Those who are not seekers, I cannot force it on anyone.

02:00:02.056 --> 02:00:04.537
It has to work out, only on seekers.

02:00:04.738 --> 02:00:07.900
Those who just want to sort of test it and things like that

02:00:08.101 --> 02:00:11.330
doesn’t work out. Those who are really seeking the truth, it works out.

02:00:11.531 --> 02:00:14.142
I am sorry, it cannot be guaranteed for everyone.

02:00:14.342 --> 02:00:16.782
If you are really seeking the truth, it works out,

02:00:16.957 --> 02:00:18.726
otherwise it does not.

02:00:19.472 --> 02:00:20.684
So these are...

02:00:20.885 --> 02:00:24.302
This is the capacity in which you are here to seek the truth.

02:00:24.502 --> 02:00:26.135
All right?

02:00:30.539 --> 02:00:33.603
L: Could Mother talk on intellect and Self Realization

02:00:33.804 --> 02:00:38.861
and part that intellect plays [as part of the] Self Relaization.

02:00:39.062 --> 02:00:43.182
SY: What part does intellect play in the Self Realization?

02:00:43.382 --> 02:00:45.862
SM: After Realization, if you are really intelligent,

02:00:46.062 --> 02:00:49.702
in the way I would say that, detached intelligent,

02:00:49.862 --> 02:00:53.102
then you see it much better than anybody else.

02:00:53.342 --> 02:00:55.262
Because you see it and you are honest,

02:00:55.422 --> 02:00:57.822
you see that this is what is happening.

02:00:58.062 --> 02:01:02.582
And you are surprised. And you learn things much faster than others.

02:01:02.782 --> 02:01:06.422
So, I call it, it is a person who has a super intelligence, I call it,

02:01:07.301 --> 02:01:10.833
intelligence which has already reached a state to see

02:01:11.034 --> 02:01:12.869
that this is not true, this is not true.

02:01:13.070 --> 02:01:15.062
You reach a point when you know this is not true.

02:01:15.262 --> 02:01:17.102
That is the point you hit the right thing.

02:01:17.342 --> 02:01:20.072
So intelligence is very helpful.

02:01:20.279 --> 02:01:22.690
And you will be surprised, we have Sahaja Yogis,

02:01:22.891 --> 02:01:25.902
most of them, of very intelligent...

02:01:26.102 --> 02:01:28.037
They are first class, first of this university,

02:01:28.238 --> 02:01:31.222
first class, first of that university, I mean all of them are there.

02:01:31.422 --> 02:01:34.666
So you meet a person who has that sharp intelligence

02:01:34.867 --> 02:01:36.142
to see things also.

02:01:36.302 --> 02:01:40.102
Also a person who is not so intelligent,

02:01:40.342 --> 02:01:43.942
but is so dedicated and is so loving,

02:01:44.102 --> 02:01:47.582
so purely loving people out of just love that is in,

02:01:47.783 --> 02:01:49.334
such people are also very good.

02:01:49.535 --> 02:01:51.540
But in any case you don’t first judge yourself,

02:01:51.741 --> 02:01:53.757
that is the first point. You are not to judge,

02:01:53.958 --> 02:01:55.465
your Kundalini knows you very well.

02:01:55.666 --> 02:01:59.301
So please don’t judge yourself, let your Kundalini judge you.

02:01:59.502 --> 02:02:01.493
Now should we have now the session for...?

02:02:01.694 --> 02:02:04.201
SY: It's just one question.
SM: One more? Yes, say...

02:02:04.402 --> 02:02:08.371
M: Is that [unclear] of the yoga before... hatha yoga?

02:02:08.572 --> 02:02:10.622
Could you speak on Kriya Yoga?

02:02:10.823 --> 02:02:14.863
SM: Same thing, Kriya Yoga is the same, which I told you or Raja.

02:02:15.063 --> 02:02:16.763
Sahaja Yoga is ’a-Kriya’ yoga.

02:02:16.938 --> 02:02:19.541
‘Kriya’ means when you do something is ‘Kriya Yoga'

02:02:19.742 --> 02:02:22.822
and “A-Kriya’ yoga is Sahaja Yoga.

02:02:23.022 --> 02:02:24.323
I don’t do anything.

02:02:24.490 --> 02:02:26.912
Without doing anything it works out, is the point.

02:02:27.113 --> 02:02:29.702
But, of course, you have to know your centers,

02:02:29.902 --> 02:02:32.382
you have to know how to nourish them, that is different.

02:02:32.591 --> 02:02:35.392
But ’Kriya’ yoga is something as I've told you,

02:02:35.593 --> 02:02:36.925
is just like ‘Raja yoga’.

02:02:37.126 --> 02:02:38.817
Without starting the Kundalini,

02:02:39.016 --> 02:02:42.204
you start sort of moving your chakras and things,

02:02:42.405 --> 02:02:44.702
it doesn’t work out.

02:02:45.070 --> 02:02:46.680
That's it.

02:02:47.462 --> 02:02:50.702
It has reached nowhere. You see, you must see the results.

02:02:50.902 --> 02:02:52.207
You must see the results.

02:02:52.398 --> 02:02:54.330
First of all when you go to any one of them,

02:02:54.531 --> 02:02:57.462
first you must see those who have been there,

02:02:57.662 --> 02:03:01.022
and see what is their capability, how they are.

02:03:01.182 --> 02:03:03.173
Unless and until you see them,

02:03:03.348 --> 02:03:07.593
why should you go to those people?

02:03:07.902 --> 02:03:09.913
Because they claim something, you shouldn’t.

02:03:10.114 --> 02:03:12.978
You must find out what are their disciples like? How are they?

02:03:13.179 --> 02:03:15.626
What sort of people they are? What have they achieved?

02:03:15.827 --> 02:03:17.679
And then go there. As a Mother, I would say

02:03:17.880 --> 02:03:20.422
what, what has these gurus given you? Nothing.

02:03:20.582 --> 02:03:22.880
They have made you broke.

02:03:23.081 --> 02:03:26.163
You have... so many are bankrupt, so many are sick,

02:03:26.370 --> 02:03:27.748
so many people are sick.

02:03:27.949 --> 02:03:30.582
This Rajnish’s disciples are so sick, you don’t know.

02:03:30.782 --> 02:03:32.702
When they come to Me, first they faint.

02:03:32.902 --> 02:03:34.644
I get so frightened with them.

02:03:34.845 --> 02:03:39.138
They faint, actually. You see, I'm really frightened, poor things.

02:03:43.022 --> 02:03:45.462
Horrible diseases have been created by them,

02:03:45.662 --> 02:03:48.102
and some people have got blood cancer from them.

02:03:48.342 --> 02:03:49.890
All kinds of things have happened.

02:03:50.091 --> 02:03:52.729
Is all very bad type of mesmerism,

02:03:52.930 --> 02:03:54.802
which you will know what it is later on.

02:03:55.003 --> 02:03:58.622
So those who have been to these gurus also are suffering today.

02:03:58.822 --> 02:04:01.977
You pay to get sick. Can you imagine?

02:04:10.142 --> 02:04:13.102
And you are all seekers, you see, that's My concern.

02:04:13.302 --> 02:04:15.782
So every seeker has a right to get his yoga.

02:04:15.982 --> 02:04:19.782
Every seeker has a right. No doubt.

02:04:19.942 --> 02:04:23.782
But if you are not seeking, I cannot force on you. I cannot.

02:04:24.022 --> 02:04:27.422
I respect your freedom. If you want you can go to heaven,

02:04:27.622 --> 02:04:31.182
if you want you can go to hell. It is very simple.

02:04:31.382 --> 02:04:33.304
One boy asked Me, "How do you go to hell?"

02:04:33.505 --> 02:04:37.022
I said, "You take two running jumps and you are there."

02:04:38.022 --> 02:04:41.457
What a question to ask?

02:04:41.787 --> 02:04:44.062
When I am talking of heaven, he is asking about hell.

02:04:44.263 --> 02:04:46.702
So, I said this is what it is.

02:04:51.542 --> 02:04:54.348
Now, finished I think.

02:04:54.531 --> 02:04:56.061
Now, madam, again.

02:04:56.262 --> 02:04:59.152
I think... Can we postpone it now?

02:04:59.390 --> 02:05:02.043
All right. You see what I am saying all these questions,

02:05:02.244 --> 02:05:05.582
even if I answer - because I'm very good at answering every question

02:05:05.782 --> 02:05:08.542
and I don’t have to think about them -

02:05:08.742 --> 02:05:11.780
but that answer is not sufficient.

02:05:11.981 --> 02:05:13.597
You have to get your awakening.

02:05:13.773 --> 02:05:17.821
That is not sufficient to satisfy you. It is not going to work out.

02:05:18.022 --> 02:05:22.853
You have to get it, is the point. All right?

02:05:27.702 --> 02:05:30.981
Now as I have told you, those who do not want to have it,

02:05:31.182 --> 02:05:33.383
should please leave the hall.

02:05:34.177 --> 02:05:36.868
There is no problem on that. I will never feel bad about it,

02:05:37.069 --> 02:05:39.258
because also you must know there's

02:05:41.822 --> 02:05:44.629
no force can be done.

02:05:44.812 --> 02:05:48.014
Those who really want it should be here and should oblige.

02:05:48.215 --> 02:05:50.353
That's being very civil.

02:05:54.582 --> 02:05:59.022
Those people who are standing can sit here and they... yes...

02:06:22.262 --> 02:06:24.904
SY: [Shri Ma] should we put the air-conditioning off?

02:06:25.105 --> 02:06:29.160
Should we put the air-conditioning off so that is clear it's not...

02:06:29.636 --> 02:06:31.953
SM: No, I mean, they won’t doubt it.

02:06:32.154 --> 02:06:34.058
SY: Just mention it.

02:06:36.542 --> 02:06:39.542
SM: If you want we can put off the air conditioning

02:06:39.702 --> 02:06:41.462
because then you should not doubt

02:06:41.662 --> 02:06:43.822
that you got cool breeze out of your head.

02:06:44.022 --> 02:06:46.222
After all your head is giving the cool breeze,

02:06:46.422 --> 02:06:48.101
that doesn’t mean the air conditioning

02:06:48.302 --> 02:06:51.222
is coming through your head, isn’t it?

02:06:57.852 --> 02:06:59.485
Actually, you see, people doubt

02:06:59.676 --> 02:07:01.601
because they don’t know what to expect.

02:07:01.802 --> 02:07:05.662
But for us it is very easy to understand,

02:07:05.822 --> 02:07:09.332
because already described what to expect after Self Realization,

02:07:09.533 --> 02:07:11.822
is described by Adi Shankaracharya

02:07:12.023 --> 02:07:14.742
‘salilam’, ’salilam’, is the cool breeze.

02:07:14.942 --> 02:07:17.782
Also cool breeze of the Holy Ghost is described in the Bible,

02:07:17.982 --> 02:07:20.702
also described the tree of life, which is this one.

02:07:20.902 --> 02:07:23.462
So many things, but you see, is not so clear cut.

02:07:23.662 --> 02:07:26.902
As it is Christ had very little time to talk to people.

02:07:27.103 --> 02:07:30.043
I mean, just imagine He was crucified.

02:07:30.472 --> 02:07:32.782
How much time they gave Him to talk publicly?

02:07:32.982 --> 02:07:36.622
I am the only one who has outclassed all, lots of things.

02:07:36.822 --> 02:07:42.062
Because now I am 67 and nobody lived like Me for so many years.

02:07:42.262 --> 02:07:45.822
They just finished Him off at a very early age.

02:07:46.022 --> 02:07:48.542
That is the trouble. Nobody understood them.

02:07:48.742 --> 02:07:53.510
No saint has lived as long as I have lived so far, somehow.

02:07:59.222 --> 02:08:01.260
All right.

02:08:03.342 --> 02:08:05.882
So a simple thing is,

02:08:06.083 --> 02:08:10.824
first I must tell you the conditions, two conditions.

02:08:11.025 --> 02:08:13.422
First one is

02:08:14.662 --> 02:08:18.422
that you are not to feel guilty at all.

02:08:18.622 --> 02:08:21.261
You have to forget the past.

02:08:21.462 --> 02:08:24.581
You have to be in the present.

02:08:24.782 --> 02:08:28.039
Forget the past, forgive yourself.

02:08:29.382 --> 02:08:34.022
Because, as I told you, the Divine is the ocean of forgiveness

02:08:34.222 --> 02:08:37.662
and you cannot do anything that cannot be forgiven

02:08:37.862 --> 02:08:44.022
by that greatness of forgiveness.

02:08:44.222 --> 02:08:48.462
So please, forgive completely yourself

02:08:48.662 --> 02:08:51.062
and know that you are not guilty at all.

02:08:51.262 --> 02:08:52.557
Supposing you were guilty,

02:08:52.758 --> 02:08:54.921
you would have been in jail. Why are you here?

02:08:55.122 --> 02:08:58.290
So now don’t jump on to small, small things,

02:08:58.491 --> 02:09:00.662
which you think is creating guilt.

02:09:00.862 --> 02:09:05.611
So not to feel guilty at all, first point.

02:09:06.222 --> 02:09:09.791
The second one is that you have to forgive everyone.

02:09:09.992 --> 02:09:12.801
Just forgive every one. Not to think whom to forgive,

02:09:13.002 --> 02:09:15.102
why to forgive, what they have done to you.

02:09:15.302 --> 02:09:19.222
But just to forgive them, logically to understand is

02:09:19.462 --> 02:09:22.164
that whether you forgive or don’t forgive,

02:09:22.355 --> 02:09:23.941
you don’t do anything.

02:09:24.142 --> 02:09:26.822
Whether you forgive someone or don’t forgive,

02:09:27.022 --> 02:09:29.902
you don’t have to do anything about it.

02:09:30.102 --> 02:09:34.142
But if you don’t forgive then you play into wrong hands.

02:09:34.342 --> 02:09:36.822
I mean actually you are playing into the hands

02:09:37.022 --> 02:09:39.447
who wanted to trouble you.

02:09:39.685 --> 02:09:42.245
So when you forgive, that person is out of your mind

02:09:42.412 --> 02:09:44.461
and no tortures anymore left.

02:09:44.662 --> 02:09:48.316
So you have to forgive and this is what is the teaching of Christ,

02:09:48.517 --> 02:09:52.622
if you remember, that "forgive them those who trespass against us

02:09:52.822 --> 02:09:55.942
for we forgive them those who trespass against us".

02:09:56.182 --> 02:09:59.542
This is a very great weapon Christ has given us.

02:09:59.702 --> 02:10:03.342
So from your heart you must just forgive everyone.

02:10:03.582 --> 02:10:07.182
These are the only two conditions we have.

02:10:11.527 --> 02:10:13.183
All right.

02:10:13.667 --> 02:10:17.297
So another thing is that we have to take help of the Mother Earth.

02:10:17.498 --> 02:10:20.622
So would be nice if we can take out our shoes at least,

02:10:20.822 --> 02:10:24.302
and keep them on one side.

02:10:33.222 --> 02:10:37.262
It is such a truth that we have so many Jews now

02:10:37.462 --> 02:10:39.240
who worship Christ

02:10:39.408 --> 02:10:43.867
and so many Hindus who worship Mohammad Sahab.

02:10:44.182 --> 02:10:46.261
Such a truth.

02:10:52.022 --> 02:10:54.302
Complete integration.